        </div>
        <div class="cert-row"><span class="cert-name">SQL 개발자 (SQLD)</span><span class="cert-date mono">2026.03</span></div>
        <div class="cert-row"><span class="cert-name">증권투자권유자문인력</span><span class="cert-date mono">2024.05</span></div>
        <div class="cert-row"><span class="cert-name">파생상품투자권유자문인력</span><span class="cert-date mono">2024.02</span></div>
        <div class="cert-row"><span class="cert-name">펀드투자권유자문인력</span><span class="cert-date mono">2023.12</span></div>
        <div class="cert-row"><span class="cert-name">AFPK</span><span class="cert-date mono">2022.04</span></div>
        <div class="cert-row"><span class="cert-name">투자자산운용사</span><span class="cert-date mono">2021.12</span></div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Additional Information -->
    <section>
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Additional Information</h2>
        <span class="rule"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-row">
        <span class="skill-label">기획 · UX</span>
        <span class="skill-list">서비스 기획 · 정보구조(IA) 설계 · UX 재설계 · 디자인 시스템 구축 · 요건정의서 작성</span>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-row">
        <span class="skill-label">AI · 개발</span>
        <span class="skill-list">Claude Code · Claude API · AI 에이전트 설계 · 프롬프트 엔지니어링 · Python · FastAPI · React · TypeScript · SQL · n8n 자동화</span>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-row">
        <span class="skill-label">데이터 · 시각화</span>
        <span class="skill-list">ClickHouse · MySQL · Pandas · Plotly · ECharts · Highcharts</span>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-row">
        <span class="skill-label">언어</span>
        <span class="skill-list">한국어 (모국어) · 영어 (비즈니스 고급 · 미국 대학 졸업)</span>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
